# IIfx boot chime — golden-WAV capture (proposal-sound-support-all-models §7).
#
# Captures the ASC wavetable boot chime through the deterministic capture
# sink and compares sample-exactly against the committed golden.
#
# Regenerate the golden by replacing the stop line with:
#   machine.sound.capture.stop boot-chime.wav
# then audition the WAV once before committing it.

machine.sound.capture.start
scheduler.run 12000000
machine.sound.capture.stop

# The chime window is ROM-controlled: mode 2 for exactly 12,516 samples.
assert machine.sound.capture.frames == 12516 "unexpected capture length"

# Sample-exact compare against the golden (fails the test on any divergence).
machine.sound.match boot-chime.wav

quit
